org.cpsolver.studentsct.model

Class Unavailability

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.model.Unavailability
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SctAssignment

    public class Unavailability
extends Object
implements SctAssignment
    Representation of an unavailability. This is typically used when the student is also an instructor and he/she is teaching during some time (and hence not available for attending classes as a student). An unavailability can be marked as can overlap in time, in which case the time overlap is allowed but the overlapping time is to be minimized.
